      BMC Musculoskelet Disord. 2009 Jul 10;10:83.PMID: 19591674 &nbsp;<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?db=pubmed&amp;cmd=link&amp;linkname=pubmed_pubmed&amp;uid=19591674">Related  citations</a> </p>
    <p align="left"><br />
